Project Dependency Graph

Dependency Tree

  • treetank:complete:pom:1.0.2-SNAPSHOT
    Complete Build

    Description: Treetank is a fully java-implemented native XML-Database. It supports cursorlike access to all nodes stored in the tree plus XPath 2.0 as query engine. Furthermore, Treetank is completely versionable. That means that each update-operation results in a new version. These versions can be easily retrieved within the database itself.

    URL: https://github.com/disy/treetank

    Project License: New BSD

      • perfidix:perfidix:jar:3.6.4-SNAPSHOT (compile)
        Perfidix Library

        Description: Perfidix comes as a light-weight Java Benchmarking Tool which allows to make simple measurements of source code without installing heavy profilers or using special IDEs. Perfidix comes as a simple jar which has to be included in the classpath. Methods which should be benched are annotated similar to JUnit testcases. With these simple modifications fast evaluation and real-time measurements can be made with existing source code without adapting the program.

        URL: https://github.com/disy/perfidix/perfidix

        Project License: New BSD
